msgstr ""
"<strong>Sørg for, at din e-handel er optimeret</strong>: Brug pakketilbud – "
"f.eks. sæsonkort + holdtrøje – for at øge værdien."

#. module: team_sports_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:team_sports_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Marketing Automation</strong> to engage fans and sponsors over time."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Automatiseret marketing</strong>, der engagerer fans og sponsorer "
"over tid."

#. module: team_sports_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:team_sports_club.welcome_article_body
